e":"2020-02-11T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOdXRpH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOdXRpH.gif&h=72a0f491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順時針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個老母好似拍過三仔"},{"pid":"55a1e5f42fc46381f9de32fcdf353230e8327467","tid":1873063,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5856468e1dbb709263d49db40d9a2f3f18105c0b","tid":1873063,"uid":194999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82512adf0ecf1abbf84bad00eba7fc3a6f3c4776","tid":1873063,"uid":42402,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"b839c82ecbb1b64ef3991eeb578f42f4d605702f","tid":1873063,"uid":93141,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"老母玩lin嗰段已經夠j 十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOdXRpH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOdXRpH.gif&h=72a0f491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順時針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個老母好似拍過三仔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"十年前三級片正好多"},{"pid":"e3dd9311685ac563c3452cb125089e525cd9974a","tid":1873063,"uid":326712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77013f61578ab2e36589a301b220f609b81a0fc8","tid":1873063,"uid":98551,"like":1,"dislike":31,"score":-30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"唔夠深層次<br />\n如果比我拍<br />\n我會喺中段開始做一樣野<br />\n就係模糊寄生蟲同宿主呢兩個角色<br />\n即係一開始窮人係寄生蟲，有錢人係宿主<br />\n去到中段就講有錢人之所以有錢係因為佢地係吸血鬼<br />\n令觀眾反思邊個先係寄生蟲<br />\n<br />\n如果再玩大啲，可以加埋特權階層<br />\n對於有錢人黎講，窮人係寄生蟲<br />\n對於有特權既人黎講，有錢人一樣係寄生蟲<br />\n<br />\n而最尾個仔見到老豆既摩斯密碼，知道老豆喺地窂<br />\n可以接一個shot係個仔喺山上邊望落去，見到萬家燈火，暗喻一盞燈就係一個被壓逼既人，城市中點點燈光就代表呢個繁榮既城市背後被壓逼既一群<br />\n<br />\n總括黎講，四平八穩，你話係咪真係曠世之作，我覺得又未必，如果能夠喺之中提夠多角度去演繹窮vs富呢個概念，而畫面構圖用上下去比喻窮富，呢度唔錯，但舊石嗰度我就睇唔明，希望有人可以講下，而剪接可以用下平衡剪接，去造一個更大對比，上流寄生族好睇，但有少少捉到鹿唔識脫角既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n利伸 尻up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"舊年green book仲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470913f3865936245417506dfdf88cdb912c09a7","tid":1873063,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a3488895d8017cbbbdc2995e4a78d7151413f95","tid":1873063,"uid":212473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd88cbf2abaae094d696e1d5337341c5d12ada9f","tid":1873063,"uid":56701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:00:07.000Z","msg":"講真屎水倒灌果到我曾經返過一份工遇過呢種情況...個種臭味真係比公廁更過份...而我仲要無得揀照入去小解(大解就點都忍住去第二度)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"化糞池浸味人聞左會暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"何止想暈，你仲會懷疑人生，點解當年讀書唔認真!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e037a80c640da423e71445492a5ad6ae35aaa0b9","tid":1873063,"uid":56701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55a1e5f42fc46381f9de32fcdf353230e8327467","tid":1873063,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5856468e1dbb709263d49db40d9a2f3f18105c0b","tid":1873063,"uid":194999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82512adf0ecf1abbf84bad00eba7fc3a6